---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="DTF Printing in Armenia | Custom T-Shirts & Bulk Orders Yerevan"
  description="High-quality DTF printing in Yerevan, Armenia. We handle small custom orders and bulk production for t-shirts, hoodies, and corporate apparel."
>
  <main>

    <h1>DTF Printing in Armenia (Yerevan)</h1>

    <p>
      High-quality Direct-to-Film (DTF) printing for custom clothing, from single pieces to large-scale production.
    </p>

    <hr />

    <h2>Why DTF Printing</h2>
    <p>
      DTF printing allows full-color, detailed designs on fabric with high durability and flexibility.
      It is ideal for both personal and business use.
    </p>

    <h2>Order Types</h2>

    <h3>Small Orders (1–10 pcs)</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Personal clothing</li>
      <li>Custom gifts</li>
      <li>Small brands and samples</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Bulk Orders (10+ pcs)</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Corporate uniforms</li>
      <li>Events and promotions</li>
      <li>Lower cost per unit</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Best For</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>T-shirts</li>
      <li>Hoodies</li>
      <li>Workwear</li>
      <li>Branded apparel</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Advantages</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>High color accuracy</li>
      <li>Works on cotton and blends</li>
      <li>Strong wash durability</li>
      <li>Flexible order size</li>
    </ul>

    <hr />

    <h2>Order DTF Printing</h2>
    <p>
      Send your design, quantity, and garment type. We will calculate pricing and production time.
    </p>

    <a href="/en/quote">Request a Quote</a>

  </main>
</Layout>